{"tid":138343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"儲備告急 中國限制外匯出境:BMW自去年11月起無法匯出","createTime":"2017-02-28T13:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T16:28:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a508b187b1139c681611a5cceb3b89f7ba3f3703","tid":138343,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:27:28.000Z","msg":"2017-02-28 <br />\n<br />\n儲備告急 中國限制外匯出境：BMW自去年11月起無法匯出在華利潤 <br />\n<br />\n2017年2月26日，微博博主「斷線的紅風箏」發佈微博稱： <br />\n<br />\n「得到一個消息，BMW中國區公司去年賣車的銷售利潤從11月起就匯不出去，4個多月了。現在是靠匯豐先墊資給BMW的外國供應商，並且告知最多能撐6個月。類似情況已普遍出現在其他外企上，焦慮在蔓延。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-CCrrgQErh0Q/WLRzkkTeBAI/AAAAAAACMvg/WLtSjmSJEzQtRFKRsXVnbBKB0SLN957_ACLcB/s640/k7yyyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-CCrrgQErh0Q%2FWLRzkkTeBAI%2FAAAAAAACMvg%2FWLtSjmSJEzQtRFKRsXVnbBKB0SLN957_ACLcB%2Fs640%2Fk7yyyy.jpg&h=6d20db2a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n博主「斷線的紅風箏」表示，該消息屬實。 <br />\n<br />\n2月27日，信息發佈者「斷線的紅風箏」已將相關信息刪除。 <br />\n<br />\n商務部網站發表於2016年12月9日的一則題為《中國限制外企匯出利潤》的消息：「中國限制外匯出境，德國在華企業無法將利潤匯回德國母公司，此舉令德國經濟界不安。」可以與以上微博內容對應來看： <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-myR-_RRMTSo/WLR0RNMoVFI/AAAAAAACMvo/bPGtm10x7jArlGIBja1ZFhPUPn9sLIg3ACLcB/s640/k7yyyyyyyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-myR-_RRMTSo%2FWLR0RNMoVFI%2FAAAAAAACMvo%2FbPGtm10x7jArlGIBja1ZFhPUPn9sLIg3ACLcB%2Fs640%2Fk7yyyyyyyy.jpg&h=f3232bb3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.molihua.org/2017/02/bmw11.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.molihua.org%2F2017%2F02%2Fbmw11.html%20&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=06d55231\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.molihua.org/2017/02/bmw11.html </a>"},{"pid":"4fa1bc7adf278f6b3655ed976f598680e6060563","tid":138343,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:32:50.000Z","msg":"賭場俾人贏錢但唔准帶錢走<img src=\"/ass